1. Posible values for category are:-
"tops", "shirts", "pants", "skirts", "dresses", "outerwear", "scarves", "belts", "tunics", "jewellery", "jumpsuits", "new-arrivals", "best-selling", “sale”, “same-pattern”, “same-color”, “any tag”

(Filter are applicable on items category and new-arrivals only.)

2. skip and limit:-
These two field should be in integer.


3. Alternate body with filter apply

Note:- sorted_by possible values : “price-asc”, “price-desc”, “best-selling-count-desc”, “created-at-desc”

{
"product": {
